Class AppointmentOutcomeRecord

java.lang.Object
com.group6.hms.app.managers.appointment.models.AppointmentOutcomeRecord
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class AppointmentOutcomeRecord extends Object implements Serializable
The AppointmentOutcomeRecord class represents the outcome of a patient's appointment. It includes information about the doctor, patient, date of appointment, type of service provided, prescribed medications, consultation notes, and the status of medication fulfillment. This class implements Serializable to allow for storage and retrieval.
